# Admin api debugging via cloudwatch logs
  1) select admin-api-v2-prod log group
  2) paste in query to find request ids

``` fields @timestamp, @message
| sort @timestamp desc
| filter strcontains(RequestPath, 'gcp')
| filter strcontains(RequestPath, 'preview')
| stats count(*) by RequestId
  ```

3) Utilize the ids to target specific logs

```
  fields RequestMethod, RequestPath, Elapsed, StatusCode
| sort @timestamp desc
| filter RequestId = '0HNKEFFS72C8I:00000001' or RequestId = '0HNKEFG2FDTB3:00000003'
| filter @@mt = 'HTTP {RequestMethod} {RequestPath} responded {StatusCode} in {Elapsed:0.0000} ms'
```
